2011-09-21T13:24:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/levitt-says-sec-should-get-more-funding-audio.html
Arthur Levitt , a former chairman of the 
U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, says the SEC needs more
funding "and should get it.". Levitt talks with Bloomberg's Ken 
Prewitt and  Tom Keene  on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg 
Surveillance."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 26:41
 